@startuml engine-manifest
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

class Manifest {
  - _path : Path
  - _data : dict[str, float]
  --
  + __init__(manifest_path: Path)
  + diff(kb_dir: Path) : FileDiff
  + update(path: Path) : void
  + remove(path: Path) : void
  + save() : void
}

class FileDiff <<NamedTuple>> {
  + new : list[Path]
  + changed : list[Path]
  + deleted : list[Path]
  --
  + is_empty() : bool
}

Manifest ..> FileDiff : diff() returns

note right of Manifest
  Persists as JSON at manifest_path
  _data schema (mtime only):
    { "/abs/path/kb/file.md": 1713000000.0 }
  Stale chunk removal delegated to
  VectorStore.delete_by_source() —
  Manifest owns only file tracking,
  not chunk ID tracking.
  diff() returns FileDiff(new, changed, deleted)
end note

@enduml
